In [16]:
def unison_shuffled_copies(a, b):
    p = np.random.permutation(len(a))
    return a[p], b[p]
In [17]:
def plot_mnist(X_data, Y_data):
    fig, axes = plt.subplots(10, 10, figsize=(12, 12))
    X_data, Y_data = unison_shuffled_copies(X_data, Y_data)
    for i in range(10):
        for j in range(10):
            index = i * 10 + j
            axes[i, j].imshow(X_data[index], 
                              cmap=plt.cm.binary)
            axes[i, j].axis('off')
            axes[i, j].set_title('labels:' + str(Y_data[index]))
    plt.tight_layout()
    plt.show()

class NeuralNetwork:
    def __init__(self, input_size, hidden_size, output_size, learning_rate):
        self.input_size = input_size
        self.hidden_size = hidden_size
        self.output_size = output_size
        self.learning_rate = learning_rate

        s =  np.sqrt(6 / (input_size + hidden_size))
        self.W1 = np.random.uniform(-s, s, [input_size, hidden_size])
        self.b1 = np.zeros((1, hidden_size))
        s =  np.sqrt(6 / (hidden_size + output_size))
        self.W2 = np.random.uniform(-s, s, [hidden_size, output_size])
        self.b2 = np.zeros((1, output_size))

    def relu(self, x):
        return np.maximum(0, x)

    def relu_derivative(self, x):
        return np.where(x > 0, 1, 0)

    def softmax(self, x):
        exp_x = np.exp(x - np.max(x, axis = 1, keepdims = True))
        return exp_x / np.sum(exp_x, axis = 1, keepdims = True)

    def layer(self, X, W, B):
        return np.dot(X, W) + B

    def SGD(self, l, dl):
        l -= self.learning_rate * dl

    def forward(self, x):
        self.z1 = self.layer(x, self.W1, self.b1)
        self.a1 = self.relu(self.z1)
        self.z2 = self.layer(self.a1, self.W2, self.b2)
        y_pred = self.softmax(self.z2)
        return y_pred

    def backward(self, X, y_true):
        m = X.shape[0]
        y_pred = self.forward(X)    
        dz2 = (y_pred - y_true) / m
        dW2 = np.dot(self.a1.T, dz2)
        db2 = np.sum(dz2, axis = 0, keepdims = True)

        dz1 = np.dot(dz2, self.W2.T) * self.relu_derivative(self.z1)
        dW1 = np.dot(X.T, dz1)
        db1 = np.sum(dz1, axis = 0, keepdims = True)

        self.SGD(self.W1, dW1)
        self.SGD(self.b1, db1)
        self.SGD(self.W2, dW2)
        self.SGD(self.b2, db2)

    def predict(self, X):
        return self.forward(X)

nn = NeuralNetwork(input_size = input_size, 
                   hidden_size = hidden_size, 
                   output_size = output_size, 
                   learning_rate = learning_rate)
In [23]:
for epoch in range(epochs):
    X_train, Y_train = unison_shuffled_copies(X_train, Y_train)
    time_one = time.time()
    for i in range(0, len(X_train), batch_size):
        X_batch = X_train[i:i + batch_size]
        Y_batch = Y_train[i:i + batch_size]
        nn.backward(X_batch, Y_batch)

    y_pred = nn.predict(X_train)
    accuracy = np.mean(np.argmax(y_pred, axis = 1) == np.argmax(Y_train, axis = 1))
    diff_time = time.time() - time_one
    print(f"Epoch: {epoch + 1}/{epochs}, Train accuracy: {accuracy:.4f}, Time: {diff_time:.2f}")

def plot_test(X_data, Y_data, y_pred):
    fig, axes = plt.subplots(10, 10, figsize=(12, 12))
    for i in range(10):
        for j in range(10):
            index = i * 10 + j
            labels_str = 'labels: ' + str(Y_data[index]) + '\n' + 'predict: ' + str(y_pred[index])
            if Y_data[index] == y_pred[index]:
                cmap = plt.cm.binary
            else:
                cmap = plt.cm.gray
            axes[i, j].imshow(X_data[index].reshape(28, 28), 
                              cmap=cmap)
            axes[i, j].axis('off')
            labels_str = 'labels: ' + str(Y_data[index]) + '\n' + 'predict: ' + str(y_pred[index])
            axes[i, j].set_title(labels_str)
    plt.tight_layout()
    plt.show()

plot_test(X_test, np.argmax(Y_test, axis = 1), np.argmax(y_pred, axis = 1))
